      <ol>
        <li>Start at Donna Nobile and head southeast on Via delle Romite.</li>
        <li>Exit San Gimignano via SP1 and follow signs toward Castel San Gimignano.</li>
        <li>Take gravel paths through the countryside toward Colle di Val d’Elsa.</li>
        <li>Cross the Elsa River and continue on SP541 toward Monteriggioni.</li>
        <li>Ride through Monteriggioni’s medieval gate and follow Via Cassia Nord.</li>
        <li>Enter Siena via Porta Camollia and navigate to Via del Paradiso.</li>
      </ol>
